### KEY TABLES FOR FRONTEND
| Table | Rows | Use For |
|-------|------|---------|
| donor_master_v2 | 131,513 | Donor profiles, search, grading |
| donor_donations_v2 | 724,419 | Donation history, charts |
| donor_addresses_v2 | 195,568 | Address display, geo mapping |
| donor_contacts | 241,762 | Contact info per source |
| volunteers_master | 13,562 | Volunteer management |
| person_tags | 128,076 | Tag filtering (37 tag types) |
| candidate_profiles | 9,759 | Candidate directory |
| nc_voters | 9,087,044 | Voter lookup |
| unified_contact_master | 9,088,075 | Cross-system identity |
| fec_raw_schedule_a | 197,101 | FEC donation records |
| nc_boe_donations_raw | 535,304 | State donation records |
| winred_ncgop_contacts | 194,279 | WinRed contacts |
| contact_enrichment | 234,402 | Apollo/BetterContact data |

### KEY COLUMN NAMES (these are NOT obvious)
donor_master_v2:
  - canonical_name (NOT full_name)
  - phone1, phone2, phone3 (NOT phone)
  - employers (text[] array, NOT employer)
  - professions (text[] array, NOT occupation)

volunteers_master:
  - cell_phone (NOT phone)
  - address_1 (NOT address)
  - zip5 (NOT zip_code)
  - source_files (text[] array, NOT source)
  - person_id (PRIMARY KEY, format: LAST|FIRST3|ZIP|SUFFIX)

## ECOSYSTEM-TO-PAGE MAPPING
When building a BroyhillGOP ecosystem, use these Inspinia pages:

| Ecosystem | Inspinia Source Pages |
|-----------|---------------------|
| Donor Intelligence | index.html + DataTables + Charts + widgets.html |
| Volunteer Mgmt | contacts.html + DataTables + calendar.html + chat.html |
| Campaign Ops | projects.html + project-kanban.html + pages-timeline.html |
