| News/Media | blog.html + article.html + pin-board.html |
| Analytics | dashboard-2.html + dashboard-3.html + metrics.html + all charts |
| Admin/Settings | roles.html + permissions.html + api-keys.html + forms |
| Fundraising | ecommerce-*.html (all 13 pages) |

