## CODING RULES
1. When building any component, FIRST open the corresponding inspinia-full/ HTML file
2. Copy the exact HTML structure, CSS classes, and JS initialization
3. Replace sample data with Supabase queries using the table/column names above
4. Keep all Bootstrap classes, custom Inspinia classes, and plugin initializations
5. Test dark mode, responsive breakpoints, and theme skin switching
6. Never simplify, remove, or "modernize" any Inspinia component — reproduce exactly
7. Deploy with: vercel --prod --yes --token=$VERCEL_TOKEN
8. All pages must connect to Supabase for live data — no static/sample data in production

